                  <accMat>
                     <p>On a slip pasted to the front of the manuscript, <name type="person" key="ArnMag001">Árni Magnússon</name> wrote: <q>Speculum Regale Aftan
                           vid eru <lb/>
                           <hi rend="underline">Mariuviſur</hi> (þær hefi eg afskrifadar — i <ref type="ms" target="AM04-0711b-is">AM. 711 b 4<hi rend="sup">to</hi>
                           </ref>). <lb/>
                           <hi rend="underline">Heims oſomi</hi>, byriaſt: Morg er man<ex>n</ex>zins
                           pina. <lb/> Bokin er komin til min fra Huſtru <name type="person" key="GudGis001">Gudride Giſladottur</name>. Var in<ex>n</ex>saumud i
                           andstygdar ledr plumpt og greylega u<ex>m</ex>vendad</q>
                     </p>
                     <p>A similar account is found in <ref type="ms" target="AM04-435-a-da">AM
                           435 a 4to</ref>, bl. 150v-151r.</p>
